replyContent: Hi Robert, alerts can be customized, by default the app notifies events with magnitude 4.5 and above, however if you reduce the minimum threshold you will be notified more events as they are more frequent. If you want to be notified about small events without receiving too many alerts, you can set up filters for the areas you want to monitor.
